<div class="row">
    <div class="col-100">
        <h2 id="migration-issues" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Migration Issues from db_config.json to Kubernetes (Root Cause Analysis)</h2>

        <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Summary</strong>: The migration from file-based configuration (db_config.json) to Kubernetes Secrets reveals 10 critical integration points where the codebase still expects file-based credentials. This section documents each issue, its root cause, affected files, and remediation steps.</p>

        <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large); margin-top: var(--spacing-large);">Issue Matrix</h3>

